videoSnippet.title: What is The Magnus Effect?
videoSnippet.description:
Have a great day :)

Magnus Carlsen vs Sipke Ernst
"The Magnus Effect" (game of the day Nov-13-2016)
Corus Group C (2004), Wijk aan Zee NED, rd 12, Jan-24
Caro-Kann Defense: Classical Variation. Main lines (B18)
